name: Cactus Heart
description:
This is the first heart in my Heart Series. This one is special because I was drawing this while also coping with my own wounded heart. During that time, I slowly realised that my self-love is so low that I often hurting myself and others around me. Just like how I let my beautiful cactus plants in my room came to their end.

It took so much times to where I am now, not that I've learned how to love myself, but the fact that I'm aware and exercising with being gentle with myself and having a more positive self-talk is already a huge step for me.

This Cactus Heart deserves to live. This might be an artefact of my wound, but this is the lesson people like me and you should comprehend. So we can relearn, reborn, and re-love ourselves.

Thank you. No, really, many thanks to you.
